FreeBSD Dotfiles
---------------
For gaming this time.

OS: FreeBSD 15.1-STABLE
WM: Sway
Terminal: foot
Wallpapers: swaybg + solid color
Extra packages: {
      grim, slurp
      mpd
      ncmpcpp
      swayimg
      emacs
      bemenu
      clipman
      ly (display manager)
}
Images at [example1.png] and [example2.png] NEVERMIND THEY AINT I REMOVED EM
---------------


Instructions to init
-----------------
1. copy every folder except emacs to .config
2. copy emacs folder to ~/.emacs.d
3. copy every file to ~
4. run ~/desktoputil.ch change-theme [kanagawa-[wave|dragon] | gruvbox-[dark|llight] | solarized-[dark|light]]
5. enjoy.